Package: ShinyState
Title: React-Style Hooks for Shiny Applications
Version: 0.6.0
Authors@R: person("Jesus", "Rodriguez Perez", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "rpsoft@gmail.com")
Description: Provides a React-inspired component and hook system for Shiny
    applications. Write UI with useState(), useEffect(), useMemo(), and
    useReducer() instead of Shiny's reactive primitives. Supports multi-page
    apps with a dormant tab lifecycle and hash-based URL routing.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/rpsoft/ShinyState
BugReports: https://github.com/rpsoft/ShinyState/issues
